"{\"uid\": \"mensxp.com-buzz-on-web-latest-167065-taiwan-olympic-legend-saw-her-father-in-aamir-khans-character-in-dangal.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Specialty:Journalism  Qualification:PG Diploma Journalismfrom IIMC  Experience:6Years  TheParis 2024 Olympicsbegan with a glittering opening ceremony on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 62, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IIMC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Institute_of_Mass_Communication\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years many athletes' life stories have inspired us to never lose hope.\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their rise to the top has taught us that anything can be achieved with hard work and determination.\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, many movies have been made on the life of Olympic athletes, highlighting their struggles and triumphs.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One such movie isAamir Khan'sDangal.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Image 1 Aamir Khan Productions  The movie is based on the life of Mahavir Singh Phogat, father of Indian women wrestlers Geeta and Babita.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mahavir Singh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.7207806123404046, \"rank\": 0.38738470885484366, \"text\": \"Indian women\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 630, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.365429211692214e-29, \"text\": \"Babita\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aamir Khan portrayed Mahavir Phogat's role to perfection, which played a key role in the movie's historic success.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1006647309888477e-45, \"text\": \"Aamir Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mahavir\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aamir Khan's character is a hard taskmaster who trains her daughters to become world-class wrestlers and fulfil his dream of winning a gold medal for the country.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1006647309888477e-45, \"text\": \"Aamir Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the reasons whyDangalbecame India'shighest grossing movie everwas that people could relate to the characters in the movie, not just in India but overseas as well.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9997032439899589, \"rank\": 0.00028634874828824134, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the unversed,Dangalwas abigger hit in China than in India.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.7677296619490023, \"rank\": 0.2985024121806942, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9997032439899589, \"rank\": 0.00028634874828824134, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"19.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dangal (2016) - Inspired by the true story of wrestler Mahavir Singh Phogat and his daughters' incredible journey to success in the wrestling world.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mahavir Singh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavir_Singh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Apple Tv)pic.twitter.com/h9oqVV9ByN    Taiwan's Olympic legend Chen Shih-hsin was among many people who felt that the movie portrayed their life on the silver screen.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999976962198323, \"rank\": 2.2391729826626298e-06, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Shih-hsin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The legendary Taekwondo player, the first Taiwanese athlete to win an Olympic gold medal, felt that Aamir's Khan's character had \\\"uncanny resemblance\\\" with her own father.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"score\": 0.9999999562410277, \"rank\": 4.375901159835127e-08, \"text\": \"Taekwondo\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taekwondo\"}, {\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9931844114083761, \"rank\": 0.004613305391635856, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\"}, {\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2349058857088542e-15, \"text\": \"Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q33999\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shah_Rukh_Khan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like Aamir Khan was tougher on his daughters, Chen Shih-hsin's father was equally strict with her, when it came to training.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1656, \"end\": 1666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1006647309888477e-45, \"text\": \"Aamir Khan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aamir_Khan\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Shih-hsin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I watchedDangalwith Chinese subtitles a few years ago, I noticed an uncanny resemblance between the wrestlers' father and my own.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1803, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9906899702512616, \"rank\": 0.005545683494256382, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My father was a hard taskmaster, much like the father portrayed in the film.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel he was even tougher on me,\\\" Chen Shih-hsin toldNDTV.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2025, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Shih-hsin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the dangal from fat to fit was real \\ud83e\\udd4apic.twitter.com/OseTi6WAWa    \\\"Yes, you could call me a chip off the old block when it comes to inheriting my father's grit and toughness, similar to the characters inDangal,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like a rebel, much like the girl in the Bollywood movie who rebelled after joining the national team.\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2325, \"end\": 2334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"score\": 0.9999999955784915, \"rank\": 4.418817928313723e-09, \"text\": \"Bollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bollywood\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But unlike her outspoken defiance, I simply left,\\\" she shared.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chen Shih-hsin won a historic gold medal in the women's 49-kg category in taekwondo at the 2004 Athens Olympics.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2451, \"end\": 2465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chen Shih-hsin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chen_Shih-hsin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She retired from the sport at a fairly young age of 25.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She now runs a Taekwondo school in the rural township of Xinfeng, teaching around 100 children.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \